      "content": "These eugenicists relied heavily on flawed methods like craniometry, which involved measuring skull sizes to \"prove\" intellectual capacity, and phrenology, which linked specific brain bumps to character traits. They also heavily utilized selective breeding experiments and biased statistical comparisons to create \"scientific\" rankings. Essentially, they cherry-picked data and invented metrics to support the pre-existing belief that some races were naturally superior or inherently flawed.",
